        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-500/70">⚠️ Dictionary-Dependent</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">UG</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-orange-300 font-semibold mb-3">3 points · U=1, G=2 · To cause loathing (dialectal)</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">UG is SOWPODS-only. If you're playing in North America (TWL/NASPA rules), this word will be challenged off the board. International players can use it freely as a U-tile management tool.</p>
      </div>

